{"tid":1639253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於幫手report被捕手足ig 不如一人做多一步提防","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:47:01.000Z","uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db69d436f183bd9993f73f4fe832f15d986ba8d7","tid":1639253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"近期多左好多人叫幫手report被捕手足既ig <br />\n雖然大家出於好心 但我唔建議咁公開地廣傳<br />\n因為個ig真係佢地本人用緊 你點report都無用<br />\n最多只係會禁你言 唔比你打caption 而唔會刪<br />\n所以大家除左要係公眾地方「我無野講」之外<br />\n麻煩大家上網用ig facebook果時做多幾步<br />\n以免比人起底<br />\n<br />\n- ig username盡量避免同其他social media既username相似 (好易起到底 睇開花生post就知)<br />\n<br />\n- 將所有個人既私人資料刪左佢 / hidden <br />\n特別係facebook 唔好連個人電話 刪走敏感資料<br />\n<br />\n- 將個account轉做不公開同私人account<br />\n<br />\n- 唔好再打卡擺上social media 特別係發夢果陣<br />\n<br />\n- 定期刪除電話入面既敏感內容同對話，特別係ig既direct message，請雙方都善用入面個「取消傳送」功能。（當然唔好係ig講敏感野）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99w4Pid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99w4Pid.png&h=785bafe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 如果你真係擔心既話，提前將ig account同password交比信得過既朋友/家人，當佢地知道你被捕/收到scheduled message後，將你instagram即刻刪除。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/csJKPju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcsJKPju.png&h=6475d5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我被捕既話 我唔會想自己個ig傳通天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左report真係無用之外 更唔想自己個ig比有心人利用 (單憑ig名都可能起到你底)"},{"pid":"3f9cfceb18e4c0bc31cc0e7f765172299047ec3a","tid":1639253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"全民口罩日 日日帶口罩"},{"pid":"8e4f424a755740f718ff349e95e3b2da7964cafc","tid":1639253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"唔好係發夢時打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44e6a95efa60ea5868ee590dd3112ba14826d5b","tid":1639253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"大家覺得spread list咁叫人report有無用<br />\n純討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0848c5ab0ed4c68a29734684185063f90439df47","tid":1639253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推先"},{"pid":"dfa1407a585756a2cf07cb5a7553e8da27cd2b81","tid":1639253,"uid":287048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"搭單問下<br />\n如果保釋期間 想改去警署報到嘅時間，應該打比邊個? <br />\n報案室電話好似唔係咁用?!<br />\n張保釋紙又無聯絡電話，都唔知點聯絡負責單case嘅CID<br />\n<br />\n有無手足知點做?"}]}